data.title: Kelly's Directory Essex 1902
data.meta_description: Kelly's Directory Essex 1902 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document appears to be the preface or introduction to the 6th edition of Kelly's Directory of the Counties of Essex, Herts, and Middlesex from 1902. It provides information on the contents and coverage of the directory, including listings of private residents and businesses across the three counties along with maps. Thanks are given to local officials who assisted in collecting the information for this updated edition.
